        <item>
            <title>【评测】Activo P1 音乐播放器，轻巧机身有 4.4mm 输出 + 听流行歌入门好选择</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/15/activo-p1/mobile-music/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=activo-p1</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/15/activo-p1/mobile-music/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:00:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动音乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Activo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Activo P1]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[p1]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1256148</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">对听歌有要求，拥有高质有线耳机，不想用手机听歌的朋友，市面上可上网装 App 的 DAP 播放器当然适合选购。但好多 DAP 机身都好重，好难拎出街，而最近来自韩国 Dreamus Company 的子品牌 Activo，就推出了新一代入门级轻巧型 DAP 音乐播放器 Activo P1，外观细小精致，便携性不俗，加上拥有 3.5mm 及 4.4mm 平衡耳机支援，可连接贵价耳机使用，价钱亦属入门级，相当抵玩。马上让小编开箱评测！</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256173 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00367-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00367-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00367-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Activo 推出了新一代的入门 DAP 音乐播放器 P1</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">先讲讲机身外型，P1 的外观时尚简约，以白银色作主调，白色部份印有「ACTIVO」字样，银色部份为磨砂铝金属，造工不错，摸上手有高级感。机顶有一个 3.5mm 插孔及 4.4mm 插孔。右边有一个开关及暂停播放按键，左边则有大小声量控制键。P1 底部则有一个 Micro SD Card 插孔，方便用家利用记忆卡播放更高质无损音乐，以及一个 USB-C PD 3.0 快速充电口。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256174 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00368-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00368-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00368-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲P1 以白银色作主调，银色部份为磨砂铝金属</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256186 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00356-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00356-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00356-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机顶有一个 3.5mm 插孔及 4.4mm 插孔</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256188 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00355-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00355-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00355-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲右边有一个开关及暂停播放按键</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256190 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00354-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00354-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00354-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左边则有大小声量控制键</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256184 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00357-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00357-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00357-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲P1 底部有一个 Micro SD Card 插孔及 USB-C PD 3.0 快速充电口</p><h2><strong>机身细小，可单手使用</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">对比起其他市面上的 DAP 音乐播放器，P1 较为细小轻身，官方表示只有 155 克（实重 158 克），轻松放入裤袋出街使用。亦正正因为机身细小，用家可以单手使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256176 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00358-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00358-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00358-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲官方表示只有 155 克（实重 158 克）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256175 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00365-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00365-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00365-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲方便用家可以单手使用</p><h2>32bit PCM MQA 无损 Hi-Res</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">P1 支援最高 32bit PCM、DSD256 及 MQA 无损 Hi-Res 音乐格式，CPU 用上了 Octa-Core 八核心处理器，搭载了两枚 ESS  ES9219Q 高性能 DAC 解码晶片。传输方面支援 Wi-Fi 2.4GHz 及 5GHz。蓝牙则支援 5.3 版本，亦支援 aptXHD、LDAC 等编码。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/455233872_2655851344-594x580.jpg" alt="" width="594" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/455233872_2655851344-594x580.jpg 594w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/455233872_2655851344-scaled.jpg 921w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 594px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲P1 支援最高 32bit PCM、DSD256 及 MQA 无损 Hi-Res 音乐格式</p><h2>多种自定义选项</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">作为一部 DAP 音乐播放器，在设定方面有多种自定义选项，包括等化器、Digital Audio Remaster、Crossfeed、LR 平衡、DAC 滤波器、ReplayGain、线路输出、音量、连续播放、及播放设定。等化器提供 20-band EQ 自定义，比一般手机耳机应用程式细致。Crossfeed 有助加强音场宽阔度，DAC 滤波器就有 7 种数码滤波器可作选择，4.4mm 平衡最高可达 4.2Vrms 输出。用家不用担心曲目声音大细不一致的问题，只要开启 ReplayGain 自动音量调节就可以了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256178 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00348-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00348-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00348-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲设定方面有多种自定义选项</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256179 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00349-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00349-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00349-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲等化器提供 20-band EQ 自定义</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256181 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00352-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00352-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00352-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲DAC 滤波器就有 7 种数码滤波器可作选择</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256182 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00353-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00353-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00353-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开启 ReplayGain 自动音量调节就可以了</p><h2><strong>续航力不错，支援快速充电</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">续航力方面，P1 的电池容量为 2,700 mAh，充电时间只需 1.5 小时，亦支援 PD3.0 快速充电。播放时间最多可达 20 小时。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256191 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00370-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00370-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00370-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲播放时间最多可达 20 小时</p><h2><strong>声底清晰，分析力中等</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACTIVO P1 主打 Bit-Perfect 播放，即使在使用串流平台收听，P1 都可以跳过串流平台的原生处理，令用家直接听到无压缩音乐。小编在 P1 上使用 Moov 播放 Beyond 的《回家》。歌曲属摇滚风格，P1 在处理上推力不算特别强大，声底清晰，分析力中等，适当地展现到歌曲特色，不论是低频或高频都分明。人声方面不算突出，似乎比较著重音乐部份。小编建议开启 Digital Audio Remaster 升频功能，「Max. PCM rate」增强声音的立体感。而「Max. DSD rate」则可以提升音场定位的清晰度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256192 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00347-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00347-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00347-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Beyond《回家》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256195 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00351-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00351-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00351-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编建议开启 Digital Audio Remaster 升频功能</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">再听听谢安琪与麦浚龙的《罗生门》，歌曲属流行歌，相对对 P1 要求的分析力不太高。歌曲音场依旧阔，低频不错，人声未算突出但清晰圆润细腻，听起来非常舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1256193 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00346-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00346-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kan00346-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲谢安琪与麦浚龙《罗生门》</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>总结：体积小，适合入门</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Activo P1 尺寸不大不小，轻巧便携，加上造工不错，外观型格。音色方面，适合听流行音乐，惟推力属一般，考虑到 P1 只是入门级，可以接受。Activo P1 的萤幕反应不错，亦支援多个串流音乐平台播放及 Micro SD，适合入门。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/15/activo-p1/mobile-music/">【评测】Activo P1 音乐播放器，轻巧机身有 4.4mm 输出 + 听流行歌入门好选择</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
